{
  "stem": "11957.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I used to take home [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] the sawings from the wood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to allow me take it home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sawdust.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So and I-- I put a couple of rifles on one of those two-wheelers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One-- the short one was OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the long one, I couldn't get it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It stuck out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I put some-- I put some rags around it, and I-- I went to the ghetto with it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hid them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hid them There were-- there were the-- also Jewish kids working-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in a-- [PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS] in a military post, which they-- they took the guns and they cut it-- cut off half-- half of the pipe and a  piece of the wood.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to take them under their clothes and-- and bring them home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So all-in-all, they had about 100 rifles and 100 guns like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we never had any experience what to-- how to maintain them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I never shot a gun before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in the woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people that were supposed to take care of us, all they told us-- we're going to go to a-- a number 15 [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] section.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're going to go to number 15 section.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we got to the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it got night, and everybody wanted to sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We fell asleep, and in the morning we got up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All those fellows that were supposed to take us to section 15 weren't there anymore, and the guns weren't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we had to do the best we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
